data.description:
Welcome to your new haven! This delightful 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom bungalow offers a cozy retreat in a convenient location. With its timeless design and modern comforts, this property is a rare gem perfect for couples, small families, or individuals looking for a serene living space. The cozy interior of this home is full of character and charm that includes sitting porches and vintage details. Upgrades to the kitchen and bathroom provide all of your modern needs.

The garage is the perfect opportunity to easily convert for an ADU option, that can maximize your living space or provide extra income.

Come see this inviting residence. Tour the grounds and see all the opportunity at this Exeter address!
